        {
            "title": "旺角男子疑樓上遇襲 腿部浴血送院救治",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"旺角男子疑樓上遇襲 腿部浴血送院救治。\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/cc1531774c4b06b3d2afeed8da8947c3/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250408/_2025040818463076827.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">旺角男子疑樓上遇襲 腿部浴血送院救治。</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>旺角上海街646-650號黃金大廈，今日（4月8日）下午4時許，一名男子懷疑遇襲，倒臥樓上一單位外，腿部受傷浴血，住戶發現大驚報案。救護員接報趕至時傷者仍有意識，隨即將其送伊利沙伯醫院救治。男子受傷原因仍在調查。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4184192/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"現場為旺角上海街646-650號黃金大廈。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/5d52f4e13802b0cc59eec3cb46b6c28f/2025-04/WhatsApp_2025-04-0818_29_24_fb93bf06.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        現場為旺角上海街646-650號黃金大廈。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
