        {
            "title": "Coldplay演唱會︱飽耳福前先醫肚 啟德零售館餐廳八成滿 內地客讚選擇多",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"Coldplay演唱會︱飽耳福前先醫肚 啟德零售館餐廳八成滿 內地客讚選擇多\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/a939b92fae0defb0ca634a5755ca2b3a/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250408/_2025040818324436159.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">Coldplay演唱會︱飽耳福前先醫肚 啟德零售館餐廳八成滿 內地客讚選擇多</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>萬眾期待的英國樂隊Coldplay演唱會今日（8日）起在啟德體育園主場館舉行。《星島頭條》記者下午4點由港鐵宋皇臺站步行前往啟德主場館，一路上人頭湧湧，不少歌迷身穿演唱會紀念T恤，沿路自拍留念，有人選擇「飽耳福」前先「醫肚」。\n\n</p><h2>零售館食肆8成滿 快餐店：內地客較多</h2>\n<p>不過由於今日是星期二，位於海邊的「啟德美食海灣」並未開檔，故部分人選擇到啟德零售館用餐。記者觀察所見，館內的連鎖中餐和西餐食肆基本8成客滿，暫未見打蛇餅情況。有連鎖快餐店職員表示，本周已加派人手，中午到現在秩序良好，較多內地遊客前來就餐。\n\n</p>\n<p>相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/society/3445270/\">Coldplay演唱會︱樂迷提早數小時到場安檢 河南客睇騷順便旅遊 預算一萬元</a>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4184111/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"館內的連鎖中餐和西餐食肆基本8成滿客。何君健攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/350eaf5cc259290f652534058cf5824e/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250408_171704636_06.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        館內的連鎖中餐和西餐食肆基本8成滿客。何君健攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4184093/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"館內的連鎖中餐和西餐食肆基本8成滿客。何君健攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/518ecadbfaa1a392d2ac7794690bef04/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250408_171704636_02.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        館內的連鎖中餐和西餐食肆基本8成滿客。何君健攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4184073/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"深圳歌迷李小姐。何君健攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ff5fe48d211ef99a744b76a28854f7f7/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250408_171734877.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        深圳歌迷李小姐。何君健攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4184081/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"來自江蘇的吳先生。何君健攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/15b961b74f40bcfef2614e7e4ee105d8/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250408_171720814.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        來自江蘇的吳先生。何君健攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4184082/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"香港歌迷Jay和朋友。何君健攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/03181250fd2d051428cb44975e754d04/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250408_171750036.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        香港歌迷Jay和朋友。何君健攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>來自江蘇的吳先生一家今次趁着來港旅遊的機會觀賞演唱會。他指預定的酒店在彌敦道，下午乘搭的士，恰好遇到一位居住在啟德的的士司機，對方對其介紹啟德一帶的歷史，「非常好的體驗，原本完全不熟悉這一區」，直言對演唱會充滿期待。\n\n</p>\n<p>他又大讚零售館內有超市「蠻好的，這個已經比很多內地體育館好」，趁演出未開始，家人更可抓緊時間購物。\n\n</p><h2>有歌迷稱價格略高但能接受</h2>\n<p>深圳歌迷李小姐和朋友趁未開場在零售館內就餐，她表示選擇非常多，價格略高，但能夠接受，「沒想到有這麼豐富的，我們簡單吃了點，食物很不錯，但有點小貴，人均消費大概不到一百元」。她今晚看完演唱會後會在港居住一晚，明日再回深圳，「好不容易買到票，來都來了，也順便在香港玩一下，晚上不急着回去。」\n\n</p>\n<p>香港歌迷Jay和朋友由北區前來，他表示今次是首度來到啟德體育園主場館，認為周圍環境不錯，零售館內售賣的食物亦是「市區價」。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4184086/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"位於海邊的「啟德美食海灣」並未開檔。何君健攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/dd7739b921ee258017a10e3c298da58b/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250408_171704636_01.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        位於海邊的「啟德美食海灣」並未開檔。何君健攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4184110/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"位於海邊的「啟德美食海灣」並未開檔。何君健攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/04024ebaca51791e7d24709efbddb0be/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250408_171704636_05.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        位於海邊的「啟德美食海灣」並未開檔。何君健攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4184112/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"館內的連鎖中餐和西餐食肆基本8成滿客。何君健攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a4d50fdbd34d89ab009ce761342cde57/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250408_171704636_07.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        館內的連鎖中餐和西餐食肆基本8成滿客。何君健攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4184113/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"入場情況。何君健攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f9842af0b06b86e2b1f33a21c5cb8341/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250408_180233365_04.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        入場情況。何君健攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4184114/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"入場情況。何君健攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/472e2fb785afcf2f9a9c279f8d00d959/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250408_180233365_06.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        入場情況。何君健攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>相關新聞：\n\n</p>\n<p><a href=\"Coldplay%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%BC%94%E5%94%B1%E6%9C%83%E6%87%B6%E4%BA%BA%E5%8C%85%E4%B8%80%E6%96%87%E7%9C%8B%E6%B8%85%E5%A0%B4%E5%9C%B0%E8%A6%8F%E5%89%87%E5%8F%96%E7%A5%A8%E5%9C%B0%E9%BB%9E%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E5%AE%89%E6%8E%92-%E8%A1%8C%E6%9D%8E%E5%AF%84%E5%AD%98%E8%99%95%E6%9C%89%E5%85%A9%E5%80%8B%20%7C%20%E6%98%9F%E5%B3%B6%E9%A0%AD%E6%A2%9D%20https%3A//www.stheadline.com/society/3444815/\">Coldplay香港演唱會懶人包︱一文看清場地規則、取票地點、交通安排 行李寄存處有兩個！</a>\n</p>\n<p><a href=\"Coldplay%E6%BC%94%E5%94%B1%E6%9C%83%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E5%B0%87%E5%8A%A0%E5%BC%B7%E5%B1%AF%E9%A6%AC%E6%9D%B1%E9%90%B5%E7%B6%AB%E6%9C%8D%E5%8B%99-%E5%95%9F%E5%BE%B7%E5%8F%8A%E5%AE%8B%E7%9A%87%E8%87%BA%E7%AB%99%E6%95%A3%E5%A0%B4%E6%99%82%E5%AF%A6%E6%96%BD%E5%96%AE%E5%90%91%E9%80%B2%E5%87%BA%E5%AE%89%E6%8E%92%E9%99%84%E8%A9%B3%E6%83%85%20%7C%20%E6%98%9F%E5%B3%B6%E9%A0%AD%E6%A2%9D%20https%3A//www.stheadline.com/society/3445179/\">Coldplay演唱會︱港鐵：將加強屯馬、東鐵綫服務 啟德及宋皇臺站散場時實施單向進出安排（附詳情）</a>\n</p>\n<p><a href=\"Coldplay%E6%BC%94%E5%94%B1%E6%9C%83%E5%91%A8%E9%82%8A%E5%BA%97%E7%8F%BE%E9%95%B7%E9%BE%8D-%E6%A8%82%E8%BF%B7%E6%8E%92%E5%85%A9%E5%B0%8F%E6%99%82-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%89%B9%E5%88%A5%E7%89%88T%E6%81%A4%E9%96%8B%E8%B3%A3%E6%90%B6%E5%85%89%20%7C%20%E6%98%9F%E5%B3%B6%E9%A0%AD%E6%A2%9D%20https%3A//www.stheadline.com/society/3445034/%20\">Coldplay演唱會︱周邊店現長龍 樂迷排兩小時 香港特別版T恤開賣搶光</a>\n</p>\n<p><a href=\"Coldplay%E5%8D%B0%E9%8C%AF%E9%A3%9B%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E5%AE%A2%E8%87%A8%E9%96%8B%E6%BC%94%E5%89%8D%E4%B8%80%E6%97%A5%E5%88%B0%E6%A9%9F%E5%A0%B4%E6%8F%9B%E7%A5%A8-%E5%86%80%E5%9C%A8%E5%95%9F%E5%BE%B7%E4%B8%BB%E5%A0%B4%E9%A4%A8%E6%9C%89%E5%A5%BD%E9%AB%94%E9%A9%97%20%7C%20%E6%98%9F%E5%B3%B6%E9%A0%AD%E6%A2%9D%20https%3A//www.stheadline.com/society/3444945/\">Coldplay印錯飛｜北京客臨開演前一日到機場換票 冀在啟德主場館有好體驗</a>\n</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/society/3444581/Coldplay%E6%BC%94%E5%94%B1%E6%9C%83%E9%81%8B%E8%BC%B8%E7%BD%B248%E8%B5%B7%E5%AF%A6%E6%96%BD%E7%89%B9%E5%88%A5%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E5%AE%89%E6%8E%92-%E4%B8%80%E6%96%87%E7%9C%8B%E6%B8%8511%E6%A2%9D%E7%89%B9%E5%88%A5%E5%B7%B4%E5%A3%AB%E7%B7%9A-%E5%8F%A6%E8%A8%AD%E9%81%8E%E5%A2%83%E5%B7%B4%E5%A3%AB%E4%BE%BF%E5%88%A9%E6%97%85%E5%AE%A2?utm_source=sthwebshare&amp;utm_medium=referral\">Coldplay演唱會｜運輸署：4.8起實施特別交通安排 一文看清11條特別巴士線 另設過境巴士便利旅客</a>\n</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/society/3444672/Coldplay%E6%BC%94%E5%94%B1%E6%9C%83%E5%85%A5%E5%A0%B4%E8%A6%81%E5%AE%89%E6%AA%A2-%E7%A6%81%E5%B8%B6%E6%A9%AB%E5%B9%85-600ml%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8B%E5%A1%91%E6%96%99%E6%88%96%E7%A1%85%E8%86%A0%E6%B0%B4%E6%A8%BD%E5%87%86%E5%85%A5%E5%A0%B4?utm_source=sthwebshare&amp;utm_medium=referral\">Coldplay演唱會︱入場要安檢 禁帶橫幅 600ml以下塑料或硅膠水樽准入場</a>\n</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/society/3445270/\">Coldplay演唱會︱樂迷提早數小時到場安檢 即棄水樽不獲進場</a>\n</p>\n<p>記者：謝宗英\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
